Frequently asked questions
--------------------------

Find answers to the questions we get asked the most about our subscriptions.

**What is Unlimited+?**

There’s no hard and fast rules when it comes to Unlimited+ plans here at Timely. Generally speaking where the team using Timely is 30 users or over, we recommend our Unlimited+ plan as  it comes with dedicated onboarding with our customer success team, as well as regular check ins designed to support you in getting the most from your Timely plan.

[Speak to our sales team](https://www.timely.com/sales-old) today to see if you qualify and get started on your automatic time tracking journey today!

**Which subscription is right for me?**

No two companies are the same and no one should pay for what they don’t need. It’s exactly why we offer different pricing plans for different businesses—whether you’re a large company, small team or freelancer.

Before choosing a subscription, you can trial [Timely free for 14 days.](https://app.timelyapp.com/join) During your trial, you have unlimited access to all of Timely’s features, so you can work out which features give you the most value.

**Can I get a demo?**

If you are looking to buy Timely for your team we highly recommend that you speak to our experienced sales team. We surveyed our customers and 97% felt they received the most value from Timely from attending a demo.

**What happens when my trial ends?**

Once your trial period ends, everything you’ve tracked in Timely will be saved. All your logged hours, projects, users, reports and memories—will be there as you left it. You’ll need to purchase a subscription to continue using Timely.

**Where do I subscribe to Timely?**

Your trial period has ended and you can’t imagine going back to manual time tracking ever again. 💃💥 We know the feeling… Thankfully, it only takes a few seconds to find and subscribe to the right Timely plan for you. To get started:

1.  Log in to Timely
2.  Click the **Settings** icon on the left-hand navigation bar
3.  Choose **Subscriptions** and take it from there.

If you have any questions, just reach out to us through support chat or email [support@timelyapp.com](mailto:support@timelyapp.com) and we’ll be right with you.

I’m missing features that were available during my trial. What can I do?

During the free trial, you can access all of Timely's features. However, they may not be included in the final plan you choose to subscribe to.

If you realize you're missing something crucial after subscribing, reach out to our [Success team](mailto:support@timelyapp.com) who can explain our plans and any in-app "upgrade" messages you may have encountered.

**Do you offer discounts?**

At Timely, we offer two types of discount:

**1\. Annual plan discount**

Get up to a 22% discount by signing up for a **yearly subscription** instead of a monthly one.

**2\. Student discounts**

Send us a note in our support chat or email [support@timelyapp.com](mailto:support@timelyapp.com) and we’ll help you out. Please note, you must provide a valid student ID and valid student email to sign up.

**I’m missing features that were available during my trial. What can I do?**

During the free trial, you can access all of Timely’s features. However, they may not be included in the final plan you choose to subscribe to.

If you realize you’re missing something crucial after subscribing, reach out to our Success team who can explain our plans and any in-app “upgrade” messages you may have encountered.

**None of these plans really fit my needs. Who can I talk to?**

**Is automatic time tracking included in all plans?**

Yes! We don’t believe anyone should have to wrestle with manual timers and note taking. You can see a full breakdown of what is included in each subscription [here.](https://timelyapp.com/pricing#features-p)

Timely's pricing plans help teams and individuals access award-winning time tracking. Start a free 14-day trial to try all our features.
